erent energies can\nreveal cosmic large-scale structure at low and intermediate redshifts. If the\nintrinsic emission spectrum is characterized by an emission peak, cosmological\ntomography with gamma ray annihilation radiation is in principle possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Aug 2009 20:01:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Aug 2009 13:52:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2010 13:58:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-12-08"}
